#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Avijjāvagga"
msgstr "1. Ignorance"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Upaḍḍhasutta"
msgstr "2. Half the Spiritual Life"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.2:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—​"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. VAR: sakyesu → sakkesu (bj)
#. VAR: nagarakaṃ nāma → nāgarakaṃ nāma (bj) | sakkaraṃ nāma (s1-3, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn45.2:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sakyesu viharati nagarakaṃ nāma sakyānaṃ nigamo."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Sakyans, where they "
"have a town named Nagaraka."

msgctxt "sn45.2:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ "
"abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando "
"bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"Then Venerable Ānanda went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, "
"and said to him:"

msgctxt "sn45.2:1.4"
msgid ""
"“upaḍḍhamidaṃ, bhante, brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā "
"kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, good friends, companions, and associates are half the spiritual life.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.2:2.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, ānanda, mā hevaṃ, ānanda."
msgstr "“Not so, Ānanda! Not so, Ānanda!"

msgctxt "sn45.2:2.2"
msgid ""
"Sakalamevidaṃ, ānanda, brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā "
"kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā."
msgstr ""
"Good friends, companions, and associates are the whole of the spiritual life."

msgctxt "sn45.2:2.3"
msgid ""
"Kalyāṇamittassetaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhuno pāṭikaṅkhaṃ kalyāṇasahāyassa "
"kalyāṇasampavaṅkassa—ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāvessati, ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkarissati."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with good friends, companions, and associates can expect to "
"develop and cultivate the noble eightfold path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.2:3.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañcānanda, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko ariyaṃ "
"aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a mendicant with good friends develop and cultivate the noble "
"eightfold path?"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idhānanda, bhikkhu sammādiṭṭhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ "
"nirodhanissitaṃ vossaggapariṇāmiṃ;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant develops right view, which relies on seclusion, fading "
"away, and cessation, and ripens as letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.3"
msgid "sammāsaṅkappaṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "They develop right thought …"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.4"
msgid "sammāvācaṃ bhāveti … pe …"
msgstr "right speech …"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.5"
msgid "sammākammantaṃ bhāveti … pe …"
msgstr "right action …"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.6"
msgid "sammāājīvaṃ bhāveti … pe …"
msgstr "right livelihood …"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.7"
msgid "sammāvāyāmaṃ bhāveti … pe …"
msgstr "right effort …"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.8"
msgid "sammāsatiṃ bhāveti … pe …"
msgstr "right mindfulness …"

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.9"
msgid ""
"sammāsamādhiṃ bhāveti vivekanissitaṃ virāganissitaṃ nirodhanissitaṃ "
"vossaggapariṇāmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"right immersion, which relies on seclusion, fading away, and cessation, and "
"ripens as letting go."

msgctxt "sn45.2:3.10"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, ānanda, bhikkhu kalyāṇamitto kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko "
"ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bhāveti, ariyaṃ aṭṭhaṅgikaṃ maggaṃ bahulīkaroti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a mendicant with good friends develops and cultivates the noble "
"eightfold path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.2:4.1"
msgid ""
"Tadamināpetaṃ, ānanda, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ yathā sakalamevidaṃ "
"brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā."
msgstr ""
"And here’s another way to understand how good friends are the whole of the "
"spiritual life."

msgctxt "sn45.2:4.2"
msgid ""
"Mamañhi, ānanda, kalyāṇamittaṃ āgamma jātidhammā sattā jātiyā parimuccanti; "
"jarādhammā sattā jarāya parimuccanti; maraṇadhammā sattā maraṇena "
"parimuccanti; sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsadhammā sattā "
"sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsehi parimuccanti."
msgstr ""
"For, by relying on me as a good friend, sentient beings who are liable to "
"rebirth, old age, and death, to sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and "
"distress are freed from all these things."

msgctxt "sn45.2:4.3"
msgid ""
"Iminā kho etaṃ, ānanda, pariyāyena veditabbaṃ yathā sakalamevidaṃ "
"brahmacariyaṃ, yadidaṃ—kalyāṇamittatā kalyāṇasahāyatā kalyāṇasampavaṅkatā”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is another way to understand how good friends are the whole of the "
"spiritual life.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.2:4.4"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
